<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #FF9800;">Reset Your Password</h1>

  <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

  <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}"
       style="background-color: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 12px 30px;
                      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    This link will expire in {{expirationMinutes}} minutes.
  </p>

  <p style="color: #d32f2f; font-size: 14px;">
    ⚠️ If you didn't request this, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.
  </p>

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">

  <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
    © {{storeName}}. All rights reserved.
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
